{"tid":944672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為風波】華春瑩：美加做法是現代版「國王的新衣」","createTime":"2018-12-17T10:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T11:02:50.000Z","uid":75969,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f03dc79469203f06382161f7fca39efae69356f4","tid":944672,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181217/s00004/526cb985d74333aa6844fc775580c2d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F526cb985d74333aa6844fc775580c2d5.jpg&h=a05ac536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為首席財務官孟晚舟早前被加拿大當局應美國政府要求拘捕，中國其後拘留兩名加拿大公民，美國促請中國放人及停止非法拘留。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，美加的做法是現代版的「國王的新衣」，並將美加比喻為故事中的國王，批評他們以「堂皇的托詞」和披上「合法的外衣」，去無視事實與蔑視法治，被世人恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩又敦促加拿大釋放被非法羈押的中國公民，促請美國撤銷對孟晚舟的逮捕令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181217/s00004/1545038032306/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F1545038032306%2F&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7287b857\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00004%2F1545038032306%2F&h=da3a2033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181217/s00004/1545038032306/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8484ede66d3b1f0f733704c12363f1a061704163","tid":944672,"uid":107574,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pD4fP9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpD4fP9c.jpg&h=0849fa39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3c9acef85e988b35e93f84cff1ff